ing: 1 (10 ounce) package frozen chopped spinach, thawed and drained
1 (.4 ounce) packet dry vegetable soup mix
des: "This is a great recipe for cold spinach dip. Serve it with vegetables, crackers or bread."
ins: In a medium mixing bowl combine spinach, sour cream, mayonnaise and vegetable soup mix. Mix well. Refrigerate it for 4 hours. Stir before serving.
